    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assemble-Ensemble has 10 fun levels, each with a different song for you to match, by showing off your factory building skills! Manage your resources and use machines to change notes to the correct pitch and length before the conveyor belts lead them to the instrument. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assemble-Ensemble offers 4 machines, that all change a note in a different way fo you to play around with.  And 4 Instruments to play the sounds! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is also a fun sandbox mode for you to compose your own little song! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have fun! </p>",
